{"summary":"Zero-knowledge proof startup RISC Zero has raised $12 million to build a scalable blockchain in a round led by Bain Capital Crypto.","webName":"theblock.co","link":"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/162358\/risc-zero-raises-12-million-to-build-a-blockchain-using-zero-knowledge-proofs","publishDate":"2022-08-09T10:00:50","id":4703,"type":null,"title":"RISC Zero raises $12 million to build a blockchain using zero-knowledge proofs","category":["INFRASTRUCTURE"],"content":["<span class=\"TextRun SCXW98061340 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW98061340 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Crypto <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW98061340 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">startup<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW98061340 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> RISC Zero has raised a $12 million seed round led by Bain Capital Crypto to build a scalable blockchain using zero-knowledge proof technology.<\/span><\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Investment firm Geometry remains a follow-on investor, according to a release on Tuesday. O<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">thers involved in the round include D1 Ventures and Cota Capital, as well as angel investors like Jinglan Wang, co-founder and CEO of Ethereum scaling solution Optimism, and Meltem Demirors<\/span><b data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">, <\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">chief strategy officer at crypto asset manager Coinshares.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"TextRun SCXW173154743 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW173154743 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">RISC Zero\u2019s area of expertise is zero-knowledge proofs, an authentication method that enables information to be verified without revealing its contents.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW173154743 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"TextRun SCXW17219251 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW17219251 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">In March of this year, RISC Zero launched<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW17219251 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> a zero-knowledge proof virtual machine, its first open-source product leveraging the authentication approach.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW17219251 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW155495053 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW155495053 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The virtual machine enables developers to build zero-knowledge proofs that can be executed on any modern computer using a variety of programming languages, <\/span><\/span><a class=\"Hyperlink SCXW155495053 BCX0\" href=\"https:\/\/www.risczero.com\/blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW155495053 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW155495053 BCX0\" data-ccp-charstyle=\"Hyperlink\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">according to RISC Zero's website<\/span><\/span><\/a><span class=\"TextRun SCXW155495053 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW155495053 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW155495053 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"TextRun SCXW170303051 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW170303051 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Now the <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SpellingErrorHighlight SCXW170303051 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">startup<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW170303051 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"> is taking this a step further with plans to build a scalable blockchain using zero-knowledge proof technology and its virtual machine, per today's release.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW170303051 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"TextRun SCXW58322779 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW58322779 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Developers with familiarity of programming languages like Rust, Go or C++ will be able to write decentralized applications on the blockchain, which look and feel more like traditional web applications, the release said.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW58322779 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW164737918 BCX0\" lang=\"EN-GB\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW164737918 BCX0\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The RISC Zero team hopes this will unlock web3 to a larger percentage of the global developer community.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW164737918 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Developers will get a sneak peek of the network in the third quarter of this year.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">&nbsp;<\/span>","<span data-contrast=\"auto\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">This is RISC Zero\u2019s second round. It raised $2 million in pre-seed round led by Geometry Research and Ramez Naam Ventures, per the release. The pre-seed took place in March, according to a <\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/edgar.secdatabase.com\/269\/191308622000001\/filing-main.htm\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span data-contrast=\"none\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Securities and Exchange Commission filing<\/span><\/a>.","Â© 2023 The Block. All Rights Reserved. This article is provided for informational purposes only. It is not offered or intended to be used as legal, tax, investment, financial, or other advice."],"entity":[{"type":"$12 million","content":"MONEY"},{"type":"2023","content":"DATE"},{"type":"$2 million","content":"MONEY"},{"type":"Securities and Exchange Commission","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"March","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Cota Capital","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Bain Capital Crypto","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Tuesday","content":"DATE"},{"type":"Jinglan Wang","content":"PERSON"},{"type":"Ramez Naam Ventures","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Geometry","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"Geometry Research","content":"ORGANIZATION"},{"type":"March of this year","content":"DATE"},{"type":"third quarter","content":"DATE"}],"hashtag":["CRYPTO"],"authors":["Kari McMahon","The Block"]}